Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.09,0:00:21.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Fui ni anata wa watashi\Nno te o tsunaide kureta{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.85,0:00:27.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hitogomi no naka hagurenai you ni{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.57,0:00:35.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sugoku ureshikute\Numaku nigirikaesenakute{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.36,0:00:40.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Koi o shiteru tte kizuita ano hi{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.24,0:00:44.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hajimari wa tomodachi{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.87,0:00:49.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sono kyoukaisen koete{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.75,0:00:54.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Futari hashiridasou{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.55,0:01:02.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mou osaekirenai nakechau hodo ni{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.39,0:01:05.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Anata no koto ga daisuki{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.73,0:01:09.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nee, uso wa tsukenai{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.11,0:01:15.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mou tomenakute ii terechau keredo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.74,0:01:19.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Watashi zenbu uketomete{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.24,0:01:25.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sou, kore kara mo zutto{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.76,0:01:44.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}"Arise Kazuki, It Is Time for World Conquest!" {\an}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.52,0:01:47.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}A professional cosplayer? What's that?{\an}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.56,0:01:50.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just talking about what\Nif there was something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.02,0:01:53.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If there was,\Nthen we'd find a job no problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.32,0:01:56.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A job? Isn't it too soon to think about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.61,0:01:58.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a carefree attitude to have.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.45,0:01:59.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.45,0:02:04.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Due to global warming,\Nthe employment market is in an ice age!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.12,0:02:07.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you take it too easy,\Npretty soon you'll be too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.71,0:02:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.00,0:02:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.79,0:02:14.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Mizuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.30,0:02:16.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing really. It's no big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.88,0:02:20.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you've been doing\Nnothing but sighing for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.55,0:02:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.47,0:02:27.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kazuki, do you plan on\Ndrawing doujinshi like this forever?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.93,0:02:30.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Uh, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.65,0:02:33.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Uchudo"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.65,0:02:36.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I get out of college, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.65,0:02:41.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Screen Tone"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.03,0:02:43.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazuki, is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.16,0:02:45.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.87,0:02:51.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The next three years are\Ngoing to go by before we know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.58,0:02:53.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're going to be a\Nprofessional manga artist, that's fine,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.88,0:02:56.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but with the way you're going,\Nare you trying to end up unemployed?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.84,0:03:04.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A pro doujinshi artist, huh?\NThere is no such thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.60,0:03:07.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazuki, are you going to\Nbecome a pro doujinshi artist?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.72,0:03:10.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no, that's not what I meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.85,0:03:14.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our goal is world conquest, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.11,0:03:15.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I was just thinking that at this rate,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.77,0:03:19.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we wouldn't even be\Nable to conquer Arakawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.03,0:03:21.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I almost forgot!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.70,0:03:24.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm out of paper for my manuscript.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.99,0:03:26.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.53,0:03:29.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you busy this afternoon?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.16,0:03:31.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.33,0:03:36.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't mind, might\NI take up a little bit of your time?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.09,0:03:39.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Yoyomori Central College"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.13,0:03:42.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Club Meeting Hall"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.55,0:03:44.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mizuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.73,0:03:52.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perfect timing!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.23,0:03:56.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Mizuki, do you\Nhave any plans for today?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.52,0:03:57.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing in particular...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.86,0:03:59.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Great, then it's decided!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.07,0:04:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What's decided?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.90,0:04:02.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haga, wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.65,0:04:04.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Sunrise Caf√©"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.41,0:04:08.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So the two of you know each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.41,0:04:11.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, we've worked together\Na little on a joint project before.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.66,0:04:14.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I'm surprised that\Nan editor like you knows Aya.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.25,0:04:16.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today was the first time I met her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.33,0:04:17.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The first time?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.38,0:04:19.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, at the last Comipa,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.59,0:04:24.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I happened to take a look at her manga,\Nand had Minami introduce me to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.76,0:04:27.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So then, are you going to\Ngive Aya a job at your magazine?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.47,0:04:29.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I plan to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.76,0:04:34.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, Hasebe,\NI'd invited Sendo once before.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.35,0:04:37.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazuki too?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.19,0:04:39.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think, Sendo?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.07,0:04:41.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like to\Nreconsider it one more time?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.44,0:04:44.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.41,0:04:49.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, Ms. Sawada.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.08,0:04:51.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's probably audacious\Nof me to ask you this
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.45,0:04:54.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,even though I haven't\Ngiven you an answer yet, but still...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.62,0:04:55.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.62,0:04:59.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Might I watch you and the others at work?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.96,0:05:01.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to watch us at work?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.76,0:05:03.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about you, Kazuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.38,0:05:05.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.97,0:05:09.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess I could take a\Nlook at how the professionals work.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.14,0:05:10.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then it's decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.76,0:05:13.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice idea. That might be good too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.77,0:05:16.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But don't get disappointed, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.64,0:05:17.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.90,0:05:22.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Monthly Gang" "Kadoyama Shoten"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.78,0:05:31.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, but are you closed today?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.95,0:05:35.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you ask that?\NOh, because no one's here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.08,0:05:36.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course we're open.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.87,0:05:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just a little early\Nfor people to be at work yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.00,0:05:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Early? But it's past 1:00!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.13,0:05:43.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.67,0:05:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In most places, the higher\Nups can come and go late.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.30,0:05:46.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But with magazine\Neditors, it's the opposite.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.34,0:05:48.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.39,0:05:51.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The executives are\Nthe ones who come in early,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.72,0:05:58.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and most of the regular editors\Ndon't come in until nightfall or later.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.19,0:06:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi, Ms. Sawada.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.40,0:06:03.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're here really early as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.86,0:06:05.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Cho.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.53,0:06:06.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mizuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.53,0:06:07.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Kazuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.74,0:06:09.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hasebe!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.03,0:06:11.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you plotting something again?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.03,0:06:13.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you mean these two?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.24,0:06:16.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They asked to observe us at work.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.91,0:06:20.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like that's the\Ncase with those two as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.38,0:06:30.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you again later, Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.05,0:06:31.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who was that man we just met?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.64,0:06:33.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The associate editor of the anime magazine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.43,0:06:37.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although, I guess he might\Nas well be called the "chief."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.35,0:06:41.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's the type who comes\Nup with unusual schemes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.06,0:06:44.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your friends must be surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.36,0:06:48.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're probably wondering if\Nediting really is such an impersonal job.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.78,0:06:51.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then the abandoned\Ncat transforms into a dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.03,0:06:52.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like there's a story meeting going
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.49,0:06:54.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,on in the conference room right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.83,0:06:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, would you like to take a look?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.20,0:06:58.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.87,0:07:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could we come in?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.00,0:07:02.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.83,0:07:05.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It really is too convenient.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.42,0:07:06.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Convenient?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.88,0:07:09.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's so bad about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.26,0:07:12.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen! If we are to win the\Nhearts and minds of the people,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.05,0:07:14.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we cannot do it with dull logic!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.10,0:07:16.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We need the arrogance of God!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.26,0:07:19.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't forget. In any\Ncreative work, the author is God!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.93,0:07:22.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is the absolute Creator!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.98,0:07:25.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nonsense? Nothing wrong with that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.82,0:07:28.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Convenient? Let me say it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.53,0:07:31.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, when the hero sees\Nthat the dragon can't step over fish,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.99,0:07:36.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he'll see right through to its true identity!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.45,0:07:37.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.54,0:07:39.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't it bring a tear to your eye?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.33,0:07:41.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He kind of reminds me of Taishi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.37,0:07:43.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, he does.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.50,0:07:47.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By any chance, was\Nthat meeting about Ostwind?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.30,0:07:50.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, do you read our magazine, Sendo?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.88,0:07:52.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.13,0:07:55.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it was a meeting about the next story.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.43,0:08:00.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I thought the\Nauthor Mr. Ueda was younger.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.48,0:08:02.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ueda is still young.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.77,0:08:04.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? But that guy was...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.48,0:08:05.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sendo...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.69,0:08:09.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you think that the man who\Nreminded you of Kuhonbutsu was Ueda?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.53,0:08:10.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He wasn't?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.65,0:08:13.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was an editor, Kono.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.03,0:08:16.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one taking notes was Ueda.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.24,0:08:17.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.74,0:08:19.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Surprised?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.12,0:08:21.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there are more cases than you think
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.50,0:08:25.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,where the manga's basic story\Nis thought up by the editing staff.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.29,0:08:27.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a particularly big trend
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.67,0:08:31.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in major magazine companies which\Nare busy putting out large circulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.26,0:08:33.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm against it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.34,0:08:37.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's because, though it\Nmight reduce the risk of a title,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.89,0:08:42.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,all manga artists have a\Nglimmer, like a rough gemstone,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.68,0:08:44.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and doing that would probably snuff it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.44,0:08:46.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A glimmer like a rough gemstone?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.48,0:08:47.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.40,0:08:49.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I want to respect\Nthe manga artists' freedom
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.73,0:08:52.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,of expression as much as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.20,0:08:56.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you're going to\Nbe meeting the illustrators,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.61,0:09:00.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,do you know what the\Nmost important qualification is?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.08,0:09:03.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it knowledge of art?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.04,0:09:04.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you're wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.46,0:09:07.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's having a tough, thick skin\Ncapable of tolerating any amount of filth.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.71,0:09:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are illustrators really that filthy?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.00,0:09:13.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you could call\Nthe level of filth "grand."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.38,0:09:17.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do the two of you know\Nhow often they clean their toilets?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.55,0:09:19.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About once a month?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.22,0:09:20.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.81,0:09:24.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not for as long as they live there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.02,0:09:27.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean, they don't even clean it once?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.31,0:09:29.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.06,0:09:31.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not only does the place turn yellow,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.15,0:09:36.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,years and years of {\i1}it {\i0}lump\Ntogether and turn into one single layer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.74,0:09:39.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.49,0:09:43.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kacchan, it's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.37,0:09:45.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Cho?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.08,0:09:47.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here at a time like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.37,0:09:51.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean what am\NI doing here? It's the deadline.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.04,0:09:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I called you yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.75,0:09:54.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? You did?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.67,0:09:56.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you playing dumb for? Anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.84,0:09:58.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W... W... W... W... W... Wait, Mr. Cho!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.55,0:10:01.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are those two standing behind you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.05,0:10:01.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Katahira"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.22,0:10:02.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Katahira"\NOh, these two?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.51,0:10:03.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Katahira"\NThey're part-timers.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.56,0:10:07.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Part-timers?! Wait just\Na minute, I'll be right out!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.27,0:10:13.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.65,0:10:18.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.28,0:10:20.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're going to be\Nworking for us next year.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.95,0:10:22.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As part of their on the job training,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.49,0:10:26.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I'd bring them\Nwith me to collect the illustrations.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.12,0:10:29.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bringing them to collect illustrations?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.92,0:10:31.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, they have school too,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.96,0:10:34.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so they can only\Ncome for two or three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.13,0:10:35.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So... Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.92,0:10:39.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When do you think you'll be finished?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.01,0:10:43.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying, Mr. Cho?\NThe deadline is tomorrow, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.60,0:10:46.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He did just say the\Ndeadline is today, didn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.02,0:10:47.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Relax!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.85,0:10:50.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I, the humble Beckham\Nof the deadline world,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.48,0:10:53.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,shall overcome all\Nobstacles to finish by tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.82,0:10:57.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll call you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.61,0:11:04.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, about that\Nconversation you just had...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.24,0:11:06.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.04,0:11:09.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I took the liberty of using\Nyou as the ultimate weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.66,0:11:11.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ultimate weapon?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.42,0:11:13.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The strongest weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.17,0:11:15.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know why,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.09,0:11:17.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but whenever we send a\Nyoung girl as a messenger to him,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.92,0:11:20.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he finishes his illustrations faster.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.43,0:11:24.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.51,0:11:28.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then if I cosplay, maybe\Nhe'll finish at super high speed!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.31,0:11:30.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.23,0:11:34.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Haga, you didn't bring\Nanything with you today, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.19,0:11:37.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He took it seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.74,0:11:41.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Comic Party Revolution{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.37,0:11:48.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Comic Party Revolution{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.12,0:11:49.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Kadoyama Shoten"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.00,0:11:52.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"First Pressing Extra: Asahi Sakurai Figure!!!"\N"Asahi Sakurai New Single Release!"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.51,0:12:07.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.85,0:12:16.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Yay!\N--You did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.94,0:12:19.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Kadoyama Shoten"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.82,0:12:22.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Comic Z Editorial Department...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.61,0:12:24.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, hello Mr. Iwaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.32,0:12:25.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Your assistant?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.95,0:12:29.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like I won't be\Nable to get my usual guy at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.62,0:12:31.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you know any other assistants?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.91,0:12:35.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a really bad time.\NComipa is coming up soon,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.92,0:12:39.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so they're all holed up\Nmaking their own doujinshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.71,0:12:42.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He missed the issue before last,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.47,0:12:44.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so he has to get this\None in no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.76,0:12:46.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, he needs an assistant?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.68,0:12:49.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, he's an old-fashioned guy,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.68,0:12:52.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so he still has the concentrated\Nlinework drawn with a pen,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.23,0:12:54.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and he has problems getting assistants.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.85,0:12:58.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Ms. Sawada, if he\Ndoesn't mind, why don't I help?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.73,0:13:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Are you sure about that, Sendo?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.90,0:13:02.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be okay helping for one night.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.90,0:13:04.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That would be a big help!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.11,0:13:05.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, I'd like to too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.95,0:13:08.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hasebe!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.70,0:13:11.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay then, please do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.66,0:13:14.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello? I've arranged for assistants here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.96,0:13:16.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Yes!\N--I'll send them over to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.42,0:13:16.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I'll send them over to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.96,0:13:18.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.25,0:13:21.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get a map and a taxi ticket for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.34,0:13:25.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, where are we going now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.97,0:13:30.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In Shinjuku, there are two\Nbooby traps for otaku writers.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.18,0:13:35.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One of them is the lounge\NTakezawa. The second is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.15,0:13:40.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come in!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.32,0:13:46.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, just walk around the\Nmess somehow and come on in.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.45,0:13:53.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th... Thanks for coming all the\Nway out to a garbage dump like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.50,0:13:55.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go make some tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.91,0:14:01.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Hobby Store"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.84,0:14:09.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like you to draw the concentrated\Nlinework on the parts I've marked.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.93,0:14:11.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.18,0:14:12.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.93,0:14:15.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, what should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.18,0:14:18.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please cheer for me in your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.65,0:14:20.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.81,0:14:24.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've been walking around and\Naround to the same places for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.23,0:14:25.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you looking for something?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.99,0:14:28.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you could say\NI'm looking for something.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.70,0:14:29.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.45,0:14:34.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today is the release\Ndate for the Super Real Series.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.70,0:14:37.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Speak of the Devil...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.08,0:14:40.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're in a place like this shopping,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.50,0:14:44.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose that means you've finished\Nyour manuscript, right, Mr. Yamaguchi?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.75,0:14:46.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Cho!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.97,0:14:49.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Writers may try to run away,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.05,0:14:51.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but somehow I get the feeling\Nwe'll be able to root them up today.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.43,0:14:56.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said you draw doujinshi?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.18,0:14:58.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.56,0:15:01.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Then you must be busy right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.52,0:15:03.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,with your manuscript for\Nthe Summer Comipa, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.73,0:15:05.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know about Comipa?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.19,0:15:06.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.48,0:15:09.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I used to do doujinshi a lot too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.24,0:15:11.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doujinshi, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.24,0:15:12.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything about it brings back memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.99,0:15:15.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you have that\Ndistant look in your eyes for?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.16,0:15:17.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's only been two or three years, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.29,0:15:21.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But back then, I was\Njust happy drawing manga.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.83,0:15:23.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I remember staying up all night
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.38,0:15:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,talking about each other's\Nmanga before the print deadline.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.34,0:15:30.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah. There was a group of people\Nwho only saw each other at times like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.43,0:15:32.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in the second floor of the printing shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.01,0:15:34.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.35,0:15:39.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you mention it,\Nwhere is the editor?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.68,0:15:41.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean Mr. Iwaya?\NHe's at the printing shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.60,0:15:42.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The printing shop?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.85,0:15:45.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The truth is, this should've\Nbeen sent to the printer today,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.15,0:15:48.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but it looks like that's not going to\Nhappen, so he's talking it over with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.23,0:15:50.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And whose fault is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.61,0:15:55.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But to tell the truth,\Nthe Comic Z editors are good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.08,0:15:58.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They must have been\Ntaught well by the Editor in Chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.04,0:16:00.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are there editors out\Nthere who aren't very good?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.87,0:16:04.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Most of the editors at\Nmajor publishers are like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.71,0:16:06.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're turning into businessmen.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.67,0:16:11.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, Mr. Cho said that editors\Nhave been really amateurish lately,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.80,0:16:17.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and even people who draw doujinshi\Nknow more about the basics of editing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.06,0:16:20.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Cho? You mean the editor from\Nthe anime magazine next to Comic Z?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.64,0:16:21.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know him?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.89,0:16:23.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I met him today.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.10,0:16:25.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that guy is something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.19,0:16:29.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They said he only goes\Nhome about twice a month.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.15,0:16:30.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He does?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.44,0:16:31.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Takezawa"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.15,0:16:35.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you allow us to have an\Nexclusive on the movie announcement,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.82,0:16:38.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we'll think about giving you the cover.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.41,0:16:43.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How are you doing? Making progress?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.92,0:16:45.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, they've been a big help.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.50,0:16:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.00,0:16:48.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I figured you probably\Nhaven't had dinner yet,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.96,0:16:50.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I brought some refreshments.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.63,0:16:54.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! That's the elusive\Nyakiniku boxed lunch!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.34,0:16:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've used up the production\Nbudget for the new opening?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.60,0:17:03.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, I'll make some excuse to\Naccounting and work it out somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.02,0:17:07.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In exchange, I want you to jump\Nthe gun on the next issue, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.52,0:17:11.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was an anime studio that\Noperates on a super-tight budget.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.32,0:17:13.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, you said "new opening"...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.61,0:17:17.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you mean they get the production\Nbudget for it from the magazine?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.41,0:17:19.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it's their payment for\Nletting us use their illustrations.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.95,0:17:25.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, the sample copy arrived\Nfrom the printer, so I brought it with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.79,0:17:27.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"A Maiden's Vase"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.96,0:17:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what do you think\Nabout holding a book you made?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.80,0:17:35.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.97,0:17:40.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To us, a book that's just been\Nfinished is like a newborn baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.81,0:17:44.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't help getting excited\Nwhen I open it up for the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.02,0:17:46.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A newborn baby?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.23,0:17:47.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the same...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.90,0:17:52.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They feel the same way as the people\Nwho take a doujinshi that we just finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.23,0:17:53.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.90,0:17:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aya...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.20,0:17:59.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Kadoyama Shoten"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.12,0:18:03.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on, Sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.29,0:18:05.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, perfect timing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.46,0:18:08.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just got a call from the printer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.12,0:18:10.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They found a spot we forgot\Nto correct in the finished proofs.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.79,0:18:12.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the finished proofs?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.21,0:18:14.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, can we make it in time?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.09,0:18:16.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're stopping the\Nprinting for only one hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.55,0:18:19.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you hurry up and get cracking,\Nyou might make it just in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.18,0:18:20.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One hour, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.80,0:18:22.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I have to hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.27,0:18:34.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aya, you set this up\Ntoday for me, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.61,0:18:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.40,0:18:37.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You asked the Editor in Chief...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.24,0:18:38.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.11,0:18:42.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't seem like\Nyour usual self yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.08,0:18:48.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it made me think, maybe you were\Nlosing sight of your goal to draw doujinshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.83,0:18:53.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I felt the same way once before.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.80,0:18:55.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.01,0:18:57.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A train is now arriving on Track 1.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.26,0:19:01.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For your safety, please\Nstay behind the white line.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.05,0:19:06.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Book Binding and Printing"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.18,0:19:08.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it always this tough?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.48,0:19:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.10,0:19:11.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,500 yen per book...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.77,0:19:14.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To us, that's not much money,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.36,0:19:18.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but to the customers who buy\Nthe books, it's no small change.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.36,0:19:21.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I think about that,\NI just can't do slipshod work.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.45,0:19:28.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it came from the author already!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.33,0:19:31.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Then we have to\Ngo collect the illustrations.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.29,0:19:33.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's okay, I'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.46,0:19:34.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.29,0:19:37.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Instead, could I ask you to\Ndo the same again next month?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.09,0:19:40.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Comic Z"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.26,0:19:41.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Comic Z"\NThanks for all the help.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.89,0:19:45.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like we're going to\Nmake the deadline just in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.22,0:19:47.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, about what we\Nwere talking about yesterday...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.56,0:19:48.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.43,0:19:50.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said you wanted to run\Nmy manga in your magazine...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.77,0:19:52.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.15,0:19:53.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, how about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.36,0:19:56.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to draw doujinshi after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.02,0:19:57.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't like the idea of becoming\Na professional manga artist?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.86,0:20:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.20,0:20:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just... There's still\Nmore I want to do with doujinshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.70,0:20:09.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus, you can find friends who have\Nthe same spirit for doujinshi as you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.54,0:20:11.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.13,0:20:18.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like I don't even have\Nto ask Hasebe what her answer is.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.71,0:20:19.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.88,0:20:21.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Too bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.72,0:20:24.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's what I feel like I should say,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.39,0:20:26.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I think I'm just a little\Nglad it turned out this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.02,0:20:33.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, perfect timing.\NWe were just about to eat breakfast.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.35,0:20:35.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we eat together?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.52,0:20:36.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were up all night, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.90,0:20:38.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You too, Kazuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.07,0:20:40.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you seem pretty cheerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.36,0:20:41.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You too, Kazuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.74,0:20:44.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.41,0:20:50.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.38,0:20:57.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taishi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.88,0:21:00.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, My Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.55,0:21:02.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.92,0:21:04.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.59,0:21:07.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do it! It's time for world conquest!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.85,0:21:11.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y... Y... Yeah!
